<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">    
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
        My name is Nick Dove, I'm a writer and a photographer living in New York City and traveling the world. I document all the wonderful and charming characters and spaces around me. Living the life of a fl√¢neur, I'm here to take notes and observe. I'm available for hire to photograph your party or anything else you may desire. If you're interested in my services, <a href="/contact">feel free to reach out</a>. 
